        <mxCell id="1c1GivEdQLBNw5b5OzwY-7" parent="1" style="text;html=1;fontSize=10;fontColor=#333333;align=left;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;whiteSpace=wrap;labelBackgroundColor=#D5E8D4;labelBorderColor=#FFD966;" value="&lt;div&gt;Context Manager - 10 tools (extensible на custom tools + encryption):&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Command&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Что does&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;cm_save_br&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Save brief — auto-summary conversation/конtextа (200-300 characters)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;cm_save_im&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Save important — structured record по by topic (до 3K characters)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;cm_save_fl&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Save full — full session log + (document) verbatim&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;cm_search&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Search by meaning — find similar conversations, even if words are different&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;cm_query&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Search с filters — по by date, by agent, by mode save&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;cm_cross&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Search в конtextе another's agent — one AI reads records another's&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;cm_agents&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;List all AI-agents с count их records&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;cm_stats&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Statistics — how many records, when last activity&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;cm_export&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Export session в format JSON — export для analysis&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;cm_help&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Show list all commands and their description&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
